other_tests.findings: Invasive adenocarcinoma, atypical adenomatous hyperplasia, and adenocarcinoma in situ found.
Identified five tumor samples: one thyroid cancer, one invasive adenocarcinoma, two adenocarcinomas in situ, and one atypical adenomatous hyperplasia.
One somatic mutation in ARID1B and a germ-line mutation in EGFR detected.
